br />\n<br />\n上網睇d盤都幾ok"},{"pid":"16af904a9fd5685f8e4f2e5d3c236c40bdf264ab","tid":157322,"uid":38936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我對搬出黎住都仲有好多疑惑嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩想問<br />\n其實我都唔係好識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知有咩要準備<br />\n同埋我係個d好難踏出第一步嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f64e68355e1263924043e89610462544a7eb734","tid":157322,"uid":38936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都因為屋企問題想搬出黎夾租<br />\n可惜我係巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祝你快d搬到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c41406624f8ead867f3473fe67deee2dab57bd","tid":157322,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪一定要返呢份PT先?<br />\n住HALL再搵附近嘅PT又O唔OK?"},{"pid":"affa770a7362fe2024bfe10168aeb08000edce6a","tid":157322,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗香港有好多打工仔一樣都係返工返到冇私人時間同身體差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n所以咪個個都好無助"},{"pid":"9d435dfcdac1a048a62c8ebe6bcef6533a4cd1d8","tid":157322,"uid":13079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"出黎做野都好難搬啦"},{"pid":"10e4ca6c53b3cc723b198077b0e186795ec05c65","tid":157322,"uid":12363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>男定女 讀緊大學定大專</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女 大學</blockquote><br />\n講你個情況一定有hall住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhall唔近翻工個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd453db1e35f7d071e3292604c718c34d99bbb2","tid":157322,"uid":38936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪一定要返呢份PT先?<br />\n住HALL再搵附近嘅PT又O唔OK?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢份pt已經翻咗好耐<br />\nd同事對我仲好過屋企人對我<br />\n唔想轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eeeeb00f58644ecb4e65279343dc925be57127","tid":157322,"uid":38936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我諗香港有好多打工仔一樣都係返工返到冇私人時間同身體差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n所以咪個個都好無助</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以香港地真係。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe279f0c26ed81f77837c00372f16ace7991afec","tid":157322,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://paultuxguitartutorial.blogspot.hk/2014/09/blog-post_26.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaultuxguitartutorial.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F09%2Fblog-post_26.html&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9195b722\" target=\"_blank\">http://paultuxguitartutorial.blogspot.hk/2014/09/blog-post_26.html</a><br />\n<br />\nLINK在此<br />\n此人自稱扮精神病成功博上單人公屋<br />\n不過上樓之前係要忍受一段住宿舍 失去經濟及人身自由既日子<br />\n<br />\n不過呢種方法好似係要扮重性精神病<br />\n即係精神分裂果d<br />\n<br />\n有精神病紀錄<br />\n如果話抑鬱焦慮都好d 至少d人聽到冇咁驚你 反正而家成條街都係抑鬱焦慮<br />\n<br />\n精神分裂真係神愛世人...<br />\n第時你搵男朋友佢聽到會嚇走人<br />\n<br />\n不過你衡量下呢個方法值唔值得<br />\n<br />\n講明先<br />\n唔包一定得<br />\n<br />\n寫呢篇BLOG條友得者<br />\n未必人人都得...<br />\n<br />\n我唔係逼你一定要跟佢做<br />\n因為唔包一定得<br />\n<br />\n為左博上樓 其實係一場賭博<br />\n而搞到自己被精神病<br />\n到底值唔值得<br />\n<br />\n呢個BLOG主應該係已經冇乜將來希望可言<br />\n所以先要咁做"},{"pid":"59e3d71c46f03379548ce99a584551ae6d4672e7","tid":157322,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"這個遊戲須要三年半以上的時間，入院幾個月至半年，等宿舍一年，住兩年以上，所以最快要三年半，大家要三思是否有這麼長的時間等待，否則這個遊戲難度實在太高了。想知道做精神病人是怎樣，愚建議大家可以到各區醫院的精神科門診看一看，大部份(99%)都像平常一般人一樣。不過，你要做精神科門診病人可不容易，排期輪候時間很長隨便都要一年半載以上。"},{"pid":"1ea7484b2f702f32a3a98253397fd29cede43f80","tid":157322,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係咪一定要返呢份PT先?<br />\n住HALL再搵附近嘅PT又O唔OK?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢份pt已經翻咗好耐<br />\nd同事對我仲好過屋企人對我<br />\n唔想轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好老實講你住HALL的話，返學方便，最遠都係返工<br />\n你轉幾程車定1-2程就到先？時間又有幾長？<br />\n你覺得由HALL去返工呢段時間辛苦啲<br />\n定留係所謂嘅屋企,受盡冷言冷語辛苦啲先？"},{"pid":"cbb5f6f8cf941fcbf1dfd656f675a8f462dd4e40","tid":157322,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"你想了解下一個所謂精神分裂病人有咩感覺<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係肯付出被精神病紀錄既代價去博上樓<br />\n<br />\n不過講真就算你真係想咁做<br />\n<br />\n過程都要成幾年<br />\n<br />\n但而家d人就算做十年野都買唔到樓啦"},{"pid":"d48d4b4b487ca5ddee766973a7b83a1efbf07fb6","tid":157322,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"講下先 點解會俾兩隻醫畜話我思覺失調其實即係精神分裂<br />\n<br />\n寫下我有咩感覺<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係決定去扮<br />\n<br />\n可以俾你參考下<br />\n<br />\n不過講明先我唔係扮<br />\n雖然我並不認為自己真係有咁重症<br />\n<br />\n但因為呢個咁on9既原因<br />\n我大學衝左返屋企摺埋從此quit左冇再讀落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e16a6edfd6b8a9c910e38612d1cf9e89c3b504c","tid":157322,"uid":74259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"大學就住宿舍啦 或者可以試下屈蛇<br />\n跟手去埋學生輔導處個啲地方問埋有冇方法可以插隊 <br />\n另外如果間學校好嘅話會另外可能搵到些小資助 最後如果成績好就搵埋船"},{"pid":"2479f57e9bf832768b5dcd96e1db028f7f441101","tid":157322,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:49:59.000Z","msg":"比五舊水塞住佢把口<br />\n遲啲讀完書搵到錢先比多啲<br />\n到時搬出去住<br />\n理得佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ee37bfe33f8ae90f948e228aca75d15a1e3200","tid":157322,"uid":38936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://paultuxguitartutorial.blogspot.hk/2014/09/blog-post_26.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaultuxguitartutorial.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F09%2Fblog-post_26.html&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9195b722\" target=\"_blank\">http://paultuxguitartutorial.blogspot.hk/2014/09/blog-post_26.html</a><br />\n<br />\nLINK在此<br />\n此人自稱扮精神病成功博上單人公屋<br />\n不過上樓之前係要忍受一段住宿舍 失去經濟及人身自由既日子<br />\n<br />\n不過呢種方法好似係要扮重性精神病<br />\n即係精神分裂果d<br />\n<br />\n有精神病紀錄<br />\n如果話抑鬱焦慮都好d 至少d人聽到冇咁驚你 反正而家成條街都係抑鬱焦慮<br />\n<br />\n精神分裂真係神愛世人...<br />\n第時你搵男朋友佢聽到會嚇走人<br />\n<br />\n不過你衡量下呢個方法值唔值得<br />\n<br />\n講明先<br />\n唔包一定得<br />\n<br />\n寫呢篇BLOG條友得者<br />\n未必人人都得...<br />\n<br />\n我唔係逼你一定要跟佢做<br />\n因為唔包一定得<br />\n<br />\n為左博上樓 其實係一場賭博<br />\n而搞到自己被精神病<br />\n到底值唔值得<br />\n<br />\n呢個BLOG主應該係已經冇乜將來希望可言<br />\n所以先要咁做</blockquote><br />\n睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用呢個方法贏到間屋但輸咗人生<br />\n我覺得唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會成世被人標籤同無咗少少自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8053bce8100db365680e1a4226dad781f76134","tid":157322,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:54:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}